<i>All right, look. This, uh,
this story on the homeless,</i>

01:22:59.992 --> 01:23:01.636
<i>it's too long.
I want five pages out of it.</i>

01:23:01.660 --> 01:23:03.805
<i>Make sure he gets five
real pages out of it.</i>

01:23:03.829 --> 01:23:06.141
<i>This guy tells his secretary
to type it tighter.</i>

01:23:06.165 --> 01:23:07.809
<i>He doesn't take anything out of it.
It's stupid.</i>

01:23:07.833 --> 01:23:09.603
<i>And I want this guy,
Johansson, off the show.</i>

01:23:09.627 --> 01:23:11.480
<i>He's not funny.
He doesn't write funny, I'm sick.</i>

01:23:11.504 --> 01:23:13.982
<i>He has cancer. I'm sorry. I'll
send him flowers. He's not funny.</i>

01:23:14.006 --> 01:23:15.317
<i>I don't want him.
I want him off.</i>

01:23:15.341 --> 01:23:17.861
<i>Jesus! Doesn't anybody
know how to write funny anymore?</i>

01:23:17.885 --> 01:23:19.529
<i>I mean, what,
what am I supposed to do?</i>

01:23:19.553 --> 01:23:20.947
<i>Am I supposed to write
everything myself?</i>

01:23:20.971 --> 01:23:23.533
<i>Write it myself, direct it
myself, produce it myself?</i>

01:23:23.557 --> 01:23:24.993
<i>I can't believe this!
Look at this!</i>

01:23:25.017 --> 01:23:26.620
<i>Look at those people out there!
Look at 'em!</i>

01:23:26.644 --> 01:23:27.996
<i>Look out the window at them!</i>

01:23:28.020 --> 01:23:30.540
<i>These people are looking
for something funny in their lives!</i>

01:23:30.564 --> 01:23:31.666
<i>They're not getting anything funny!</i>

01:23:31.690 --> 01:23:32.959
<i>You're giving them straight lines!</i>

01:23:32.983 --> 01:23:34.795
<i>Their lives are
straight lines already.</i>

01:23:34.819 --> 01:23:36.219
<i>They're waiting for
something funny!</i>

01:23:54.463 --> 01:23:55.965
This is terrible.

01:23:56.507 --> 01:23:58.009
What are you doing to me?

01:23:58.717 --> 01:24:01.561
This is supposed to be the
profile of a creative mind.

01:24:01.887 --> 01:24:03.990
<i>It's very tough for a woman
in this profession.</i>

01:24:04.014 --> 01:24:05.408
<i>I mean,
men are always hitting on you.</i>

01:24:05.432 --> 01:24:07.119
<i>I can make it easier for you...</i>

